150→+# In-Game Mail Implementation Plan
151→+
152→+> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.
153→+
154→+**Goal:** Add text-only in-game mail support — list, read, send, delete via /mail commands.
155→+
156→+**Architecture:** Protocol parsing in `src/wow/protocol/mail.ts`, handlers in `world-handlers.ts`, state on WorldConn, commands in both TUI and daemon paths. Follows the existing guild roster request/response pattern.
157→+
158→+**Tech Stack:** TypeScript, Bun, PacketReader/PacketWriter
